<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        border-top-left-radius: 8px;
        border-top-right-radius: 8px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border-left: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .feature-list {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      .feature-list li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Playground!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Your account is now fully activated!</strong> Thank you for joining Playground by Flukebase. We're thrilled to have you as part of our experimental language learning community.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        With your verified account, you now have full access to our innovative language learning platform designed for flexibility and clear feedback.
      </p>
      
      <div class="feature-list">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #4f46e5;">Your New Features</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Realtime AI Conversations</strong> - Practice speaking naturally with our AI language partners that adapt to your level</li>
          <li><strong>Audio Transcription</strong> - Upload recordings and get detailed pronunciation feedback</li>
          <li><strong>Practice History</strong> - Track your progress with detailed session history</li>
          <li><strong>Performance Analytics</strong> - Visualize your improvement over time with our analytics dashboard</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        Ready to start your language learning journey? Click below to log in and begin exploring:
      </p>
      
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Start Exploring Now</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        We recommend starting with a quick conversation in our Realtime module to get familiar with how Playground works.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance getting started, our support team is ready to help at <a href="mailto:support@flukebase.me" style="color: #4f46e5;">support@flukebase.me</a>.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Happy learning!<br>
        <strong>The Flukebase Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Flukebase. All rights reserved.<br>
        You're receiving this email because you signed up for Playground.<br>
        <a href="#" style="color: #6b7280;">Manage email preferences</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
